WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.187
To fully weaponize this ecosystem, you must understand the underlying

00:00:04.187 --> 00:00:08.374
financial mechanics of why a giant like Amazon actively invests

00:00:08.374 --> 00:00:12.561
in our ongoing growth. This relationship is a highly calculated,

00:00:12.561 --> 00:00:16.747
mutually beneficial growth engine explicitly rooted in annual recurring revenue.

00:00:16.747 --> 00:00:20.934
AppsFlyer is a major, resource-intensive customer of their infrastructure, meaning

00:00:20.934 --> 00:00:25.121
that when our platform scales and our global customer base

00:00:25.121 --> 00:00:29.308
expands, our underlying cloud utilization predictably increases, which directly expands

00:00:29.308 --> 00:00:33.495
Amazon's bottom line.
